1) Install tools + Vulkan deps (Ubuntu/Debian)
sudo apt update
sudo apt install -y build-essential cmake ninja-build git pkg-config \
  libvulkan-dev vulkan-tools glslang-tools vulkan-utility-libraries-dev

Sanity check:

ninja --version
g++ --version
vulkaninfo --summary
glslangValidator --version
2) Clone + build starting-point-2 (the one you edit)
git clone https://github.com/vblanco20-1/vulkan-guide.git
cd vulkan-guide
git checkout starting-point-2

cmake -S . -B build -G Ninja -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug
cmake --build build -j"$(nproc)"
./bin/engine

When you change shaders:

cmake --build build --target Shaders
./bin/engine